<paragraph pageId="691" pageNumber="692">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Casey" authorityYear="1914" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Pharalus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="691" pageNumber="692" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Pharalus</taxonomicName>
Casey, 1914: 68. Type species: 
